00:13:05.670 --> 00:13:10.380 align:middle line:84%
accommodation to a
flawed parent, rebellion

00:13:10.380 --> 00:13:13.470 align:middle line:84%
as a protest against a
flawed parent, and three,

00:13:13.470 --> 00:13:15.090 align:middle line:90%
