00:14:13.470 --> 00:14:16.020 align:middle line:84%
inept socially, did
poorly with women.

00:14:16.020 --> 00:14:20.070 align:middle line:84%
And he couldn't wait to have a
son fulfill his own fantasies

00:14:20.070 --> 00:14:22.680 align:middle line:90%
by being a great ladies' man.

00:14:22.680 --> 00:14:25.410 align:middle line:84%
It would be very difficult
