00:14:31.842 --> 00:14:33.800 align:middle line:84%
Otherwise, you'd be
disappointing your father's

00:14:33.800 --> 00:14:36.050 align:middle line:90%
needs for great conquests.

00:14:36.050 --> 00:14:37.490 align:middle line:90%
That would be second.

00:14:37.490 --> 00:14:41.212 align:middle line:84%
The third would be if you had a
parent who was very rejecting.

00:14:41.212 --> 00:14:42.170 align:middle line:90%
Let's say you're a boy.

00:14:42.170 --> 00:14:45.140 align:middle line:84%
And you had a very
rejecting mother.

00:14:45.140 --> 00:14:48.290 align:middle line:84%
Every time you tried to
be close, she'd push away.

00:14:48.290 --> 00:14:50.680 align:middle line:90%
