00:15:04.700 --> 00:15:06.710 align:middle line:90%
So that's based on rejection.

00:15:06.710 --> 00:15:11.420 align:middle line:84%
The second category--
rebellion as a protest.

00:15:11.420 --> 00:15:13.550 align:middle line:84%
If you came from
