00:15:40.730 --> 00:15:41.540 align:middle line:84%
And I'm never going
to let myself be--

00:15:41.540 --> 00:15:42.707 align:middle line:90%
>> And be scandalous, right?

00:15:42.707 --> 00:15:44.360 align:middle line:90%
>> Scandalous.

00:15:44.360 --> 00:15:49.150 align:middle line:84%
Now, the two next areas which
are very, very important

00:15:49.150 --> 00:15:51.700 align:middle line:84%
to your question
