00:16:28.570 --> 00:16:29.020 align:middle line:90%
or you--

00:16:29.020 --> 00:16:30.020 align:middle line:90%
>> And she devoured you.

00:16:30.020 --> 00:16:31.240 align:middle line:90%
>> She devoured you.

00:16:31.240 --> 00:16:35.260 align:middle line:84%
And your guilt also
