00:16:38.812 --> 00:16:40.020 align:middle line:90%
So that would be a rebellion.

00:16:40.020 --> 00:16:40.820 align:middle line:90%
Have many.

00:16:40.820 --> 00:16:43.960 align:middle line:84%
You'd not allow yourself
