00:16:49.330 --> 00:16:52.900 align:middle line:84%
might feel that there was
a burden to cheer her up,

00:16:52.900 --> 00:16:54.460 align:middle line:90%
to make her happy.

00:16:54.460 --> 00:16:57.430 align:middle line:84%
And you again don't want to be
trapped into being a caretaker.

00:16:57.430 --> 00:16:59.050 align:middle line:90%
So you run the other way.

00:16:59.050 --> 00:17:01.630 align:middle line:84%
In "Marvin's Room," we
talked about that, the, movie

00:17:01.630 --> 00:17:03.250 align:middle line:90%
