00:17:52.570 --> 00:17:53.750 align:middle line:90%
Why does that happen?

00:17:53.750 --> 00:17:57.040 align:middle line:84%
One, you don't want to
remember the unpleasantness

00:17:57.040 --> 00:18:01.000 align:middle line:84%
