00:18:19.240 --> 00:18:20.860 align:middle line:90%
He was always having affairs.

00:18:20.860 --> 00:18:22.750 align:middle line:84%
So it might be
difficult for a son

00:18:22.750 --> 00:18:24.860 align:middle line:84%
to actually better his
