being committed and serious

00:18:37.468 --> 00:18:39.010 align:middle line:84%
and why they would
run the other way,

00:18:39.010 --> 00:18:42.070 align:middle line:84%
why would they be
scared, why it would

00:18:42.070 --> 00:18:45.610 align:middle line:84%
